name: Phantasy Star Online 2 New Genesis: Aelio Nadar Deluxe Edition
summary:
Contains the Aelio Nadar swimsuit outfit, perfect for the stunning beaches of Aelio, as well as various support items. This is a great bargain, which can only be purchased once per each platform!

・The core game is Free-to-Play, but there is certain paid content that can be purchased.
